general.desc: EasyCall Communications Philippines Inc is engaged in information technology-related business. It operates as an Internet Services Provider in the Philippines. The company's products and services include customer service, corporate digital subscriber line resellership, Internet service, Web business solutions and server co-location. It also offers Internet protocol broadband managed services through a very small aperture terminal.
